        <mxCell id="zqkSzmjsO5AOMt-KT8qr-26" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;personal preferences&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;/ˈpɜːsənl ˈprefərənsɪz/&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;Designing user interfaces that accommodate personal preferences can significantly enhance user satisfaction and usability&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;" vertex="1" parent="1">
